reviewText: Better and more informative offerings on YouTube for free.
A little boring but it does have all the main sights on Bangkok. Worth seeing if your planning a trip to Thailand.

While I plan to be in Bangkok for 2 weeks and this seems a long time, I researched the city so I could plan the tours and sights I must see to get the most out of my time. I also planned free days to travel about the city on my own. The video was colorful, informative and I was able to pre-visit many of the sights, so I was able to decide which ones I wanted to see in person.
